Package com.microblink.blinkid.activity.result

Class BaseScanResult<T>

java.lang.Object
com.microblink.blinkid.activity.result.BaseScanResult<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
OneSideScanResult, ScanResult, TwoSideScanResult
public abstract class BaseScanResult<T> extends Object
Result of the scanning process. You should first check the result status by using the getResultStatus(). If it is ResultStatus.FINISHED, data will be available in the returned BaseScanResult data object, otherwise it will be null.
